column3: Please advise how I get a CLA arranged.
Could you please share your e-mail address, and I'll send you the CLA form to sign electronically.

Alternatively, you may download the PDF from http://www.jetbrains.org/display/IJOS/Contributor+Agreement and then print it out, sign (mention you github account name there), scan and email to contribute@jetbrains.com
We would also like to request you to update your commit authorship with your actual e-mail address instead of @users.noreply.github.com.
@allanlewis Please make a PR in https://github.com/JetBrains/python-skeletons repository. Folder in current repo is a mirror, we sync it manually.
Hello! https://github.com/JetBrains/python-skeletons repository is deprecated. We're on our way to support pyi-stubs. Please check typeshed repository and send PR there if needed.
